cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper focuses on emotion recognition using both lexical and acoustic modalities, which falls under the categories of speech processing (cs.SD), natural language processing (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of multimodal models (cs.MM) and multi-view learning techniques to improve the accuracy of emotion recognition.
